<div class="language-sql ext-sql line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="shiki" style="background-color: #212121"><code><span class="line"><span style="color: #545454; font-style: italic">-- 查询地址中倒数第二个字是&#39;西&#39;字的用户信息</span></span>
