<div class="language-sql ext-sql line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="shiki" style="background-color: #212121"><code><span class="line"><span style="color: #545454; font-style: italic">-- 查询用户的平均年龄是多少?</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #F78C6C">SELECT</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #82AAFF">AVG</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">(age) </span><span style="color: #F78C6C">FROM</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #89DDFF">`</span><span style="color: #C3E88D">user</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">`</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">;</span></span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="sum-求和" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#sum-求和" aria-hidden="true">#</a> <strong><code v-pre>SUM( )</code></strong> 求和</h3>
<div class="language-sql ext-sql line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="shiki" style="background-color: #212121"><code><span class="line"><span style="color: #545454; font-style: italic">-- 查询用户的工资总和</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #F78C6C">SELECT</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #82AAFF">SUM</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">(sal) </span><span style="color: #F78C6C">FROM</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #89DDFF">`</span><span style="color: #C3E88D">user</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">`</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">;</span></span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="分页-limit" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#分页-limit" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 分页 <strong><code v-pre>LIMIT</code></strong></h2>
<p><strong><code v-pre>LIMIT num1，num2</code></strong> 通过分页可以将数据分页，前端实际应用在<code v-pre>翻页</code></p>
<div class="custom-container tip"><p class="custom-container-title">TIP</p>
